{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"705aadce98","title":"读《读通鉴论》批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d4d3a29742","type":"title","text":"读《读通鉴论》批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"db23e32cfc","type":"subtitle","text":"读《读通鉴论》批语","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"d59c244a2c","type":"paragraph","text":"拓拔宏授位于子，而自称太上皇帝，子幼而","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"28a3ff8c16","type":"paragraph","text":"恐为人所复夺也。....宏好黄老，而得老氏之","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"e191498c6b","type":"paragraph","text":"术。其欲逊位于子推也，老氏欲取固与之术也。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"57a5cc1d14","type":"paragraph","text":"其托于清磁，而其建立耐子之旨也，老氏守兑","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"0725dc2135","type":"paragraph","text":"之术也。所欲立者非不正，而施道行之，巧笼宗","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"71425d21eb","type":"paragraph","text":"室大臣之心，亦校奖战！而抑包君人之道战？虽","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"c691915c15","type":"paragraph","text":"申韩未必皆然，其以传位笼子推而制之，犹贤于宋明帝之赋贼杀，如曹操、杀兄弟，以安其养子远兵！黄老之术，所由贤子","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"727aa79a26","type":"paragraph","text":"申韩也。然而疑虑以钳制天下，则一也。故日，刘备、诸葛。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"9d269367b4","type":"paragraph","text":"黄老之流为申韩，机诈兴而末流极于残忍，故君","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"05c5285419","type":"paragraph","text":"子重恶之也。[卷十五《宋明帝》第35页]","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"47812c2cd5","type":"paragraph","text":"若夫坏人心，乱风俗，酿盗贼赛就危亡之福","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"18300972a6","type":"paragraph","text":"儒俗者万者，莫烈于俗儒。俗儒者，以干禄之部夫为师者千，而贤者不也，教以利，学以利，利乃沁入于人心，而不知一，不如过去法何者之为君父，因异端之所不屑者也。......俗儒家之犹讲一些真奉章程以希利达，师部夫而学部夫，非放豚也，话。儒非徒柔也，乃押虎也，驱之而已奖，又何受为？「卷十七","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"17658a9652","type":"paragraph","text":"《梁武帝》第6页]尤为伪者骗也","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"403c078ac7","type":"paragraph","text":"佛老之于申韩，犹鼓之相应也。应之以申","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"a707042e59","type":"paragraph","text":"韩，而与治道弥相近奖。汉之所谓酷更，后世之","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"60bf105cdd","type":"paragraph","text":"所谓贤臣也。至是而民之弱者死，强者冠，民乃","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"79c288b026","type":"paragraph","text":"韩，故朱异以亡梁，王安石、张商英以乱宋。何","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"fc24ed463c","type":"paragraph","text":"其教孔孟，以珍而国乃以亡。鸣呼！其教佛老者，其法必申","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"a22a8a9b83","type":"paragraph","text":"也？虚寂之甚，百为必无以应用，一委于一切之其法亦必申韩。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"e1c416e09c","type":"paragraph","text":"法，督责天下以自逸，而后心以不操而自速。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"},{"id":"f649301148","type":"paragraph","text":"[卷十七《梁武帝》第24页]","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98"}],"page":{"id":"824f45a4e5","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"705aadce98","start":448,"end":451}}}},"__N_SSG":true}